<p>
<lb n="1"/><unclear>svasti</unclear> śakavarṣaṁbulu 107<unclear>3</unclear> gu nēṇṭi Utta rāya 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>nasaṁkrāṁtti nimittamuna śrī manmahāmaṇḍa lēśva 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ra kolani kāṭamanāyakuṇḍu vadminīpuraṁbuna 
<lb n="4"/>śrī svarnnēśvaramahādēvarakuṁ beṭṭina Akhaṇḍa va<unclear>r</unclear>tti 
<lb n="5"/>dīpa mokkoṇṭiki 1 niccina yinupaye ḍleṁbadi 50 vī 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>niṁ jēkoni pulluḍutapāṁḍipaḍa<unclear>pa</unclear>nayeṟi 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>yamavōyuṇḍu sāniyaṁbāṭi nitya mā 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>neṇḍu neyi Ācaṁdrā<unclear>r</unclear>kamuṁ butrānu 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>pautrikamugā saliyiṁpaṁgalavāru 
</p>

